CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 12, 1941, pg. 18, reads: "Pictured here are the young ladies who won prizes in bathing beauty contest last Friday sponsored by the Business and Professional Men's Association in Pittsburgh at their annual South Park picnic...Miss Ernestine Holloway, right, who won 2nd prize at the highly competitive contest. - Harris photo"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Ernestine Holloway wearing two-piece bathing suit with sash reading "Princess Beauty ...," holding second place trophy and standing at Sully's pool in South Park for Business and Professional Men's Association picnic
